headline: Ralph Lauren: price target raised at Jefferies
summary: Jefferies reaffirms its 'buy' recommendation on Ralph Lauren, with a price target raised by 14% to $280, in a note devoted to the 2025 outlook for US fashion players.Ralph Lauren remains a favorite...
